Class Memory

  • java.lang.Object
    • objenome.AbstractPrototainer
      • objenome.Container
        • nars.Param
          • nars.Memory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Level, AbstractContainer, Prototainer

    public class Memory
extends Param
    Memory consists of the run-time state of a NAR, including: * term and concept memory * clock * reasoner state * etc.

    Excluding input/output channels which are managed by a NAR.

    A memory is controlled by zero or one NAR's at a given time.

    Memory is serializable so it can be persisted and transported.
